snippet.title: Dynamic Duo | Healthy Relaxed Hair | Amber Rose Shampoo & Conditioner
snippet.description:
Hey, guys!  Well, I just could not “hold my horses” on this one!  I tried a new shampoo and conditioner on my relaxed hair and am spilling the beans on the final results!  So anyone looking to add to their arsenal... this product review is for you!

Enjoy and thanks for watching! ♥️
